<h3>HP Pavilion laptop drivers.</h3>
<div class="postmsg">
<p>This is a general question regarding the ability or inability to manually install specific drivers for an HP laptop on Linux. I.E; (BIOS updates, possible HDD firmware or Intel CPU firmware.) </p><p>I know on Windows at least they have a page specifically for it, but I was wondering if anybody knew of another way. Probably terminal.</p>
