<div class="postright">
<h3>Re: HP Pavilion laptop drivers.</h3>
<div class="postmsg">
<p>HP drivers are not going to be easy to install.&#160; However when asking how to install drivers please list the drivers so we all know which ones.&#160; Graphic drivers especially the most of them do come pre-installed with the distribution.&#160; Please do not confuse Linux and Windows. Because all drivers that come for HP are .EXE files which are not compatible with Linux.</p>
</div>
<div class="postsignature postmsg"><hr/><p>-Jeff Szydel </p><p>*Parrot Ambassador&#160; &#160;*Social Groups Manager&#160; &#160;*Helpdesk&#160; &#160;*Wiki Editor&#160; &#160; <br/>*Parrot Telegram Group Administrator&#160; &#160;*Parrot Community Administrator</p></div>
