<h3>Re: HP Pavilion laptop drivers.</h3>
<div class="postmsg">
<p>I&#039;m very much aware that Windows EXE files won&#039;t even remotely work on Linux the same. As for specific drivers? Intel CPU firmware? Intel GPU driver? (Built in to the CPU)</p><p>Synaptics touchpad driver as well. <a href="http://h20564.www2.hp.com/hpsc/swd/public/detail?swItemId=ob_45999_1" rel="nofollow">http://h20564.www2.hp.com/hpsc/swd/publ â€¦ ob_45999_1</a></p>
